>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1>Is Crazy Time Rigged? The Truth for 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-slate-300">
      The short answer: No. Crazy Time uses a physical certified wheel operated by Evolution Gaming under regulated gambling licenses. Here is the evidence and how to verify it yourself.
