      <li>Look for the independent testing lab certification (eCOGRA seal is common)</li>
      <li>Only play on licensed platforms like Stake, which is regulated and audited</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>The Real Risk: House Edge</h2>
    <p>
      The wheel is not rigged — but the house edge is real. Every segment has an RTP below 100%. This is the legitimate, transparent advantage the casino holds. It is not cheating — it is the cost of playing. Read the <a href="/crazy-time-rtp">RTP breakdown</a> to understand exactly what the house edge is per segment.
    </p>

    <StakeCTA variant="card" text="Play Crazy Time on Stake — Licensed & Certified →" />

